sequenceDiagram
  participant Dev as Developer
  participant SvcRepo as CANFAR service repo CI
  participant Harbor as Harbor
  participant Auto as RC deploy automation
  participant KeelDeploy as keel-deploy
  participant Argo as Argo CD
  participant Staging as canfar-system-staging

  Dev->>SvcRepo: Merge RC branch / tag
  SvcRepo->>Harbor: Publish chart/image with -rc.N tag
  Harbor->>Auto: Webhook or poll on new RC artifact
  Auto->>KeelDeploy: PR or bot commit bumps staging targetRevision/image.tag
  KeelDeploy->>Argo: Merge to main
  Argo->>Staging: Sync canfar.net staging Applications
